Usage
-----

Hard-coded port is 4848 and a simple 

    telnet localhost 4848
    
will return a netstat listing. No IP whitelisting or any form of configuration right now.

Dependencies
------------

On Debian run

   apt-get install build-essential libevent-dev libglib2.0-dev
   

Building
--------

- autoreconf -i
- ./configure
- make && make install
